===Proper noun===
'''Hokkien'''

#a dialect of the Chinese language which is mainly spoken in the south-eastern part of Mainland China, [[Fujian]], in [[Taiwan]], by the Chinese minorities in [[Southeast Asia]] and by many [[overseas Chinese]] worldwide.

===Synonyms===
*[[Min Nan]], Southern Min, Hoklo, and [[Taiwanese]].

====Translations====
